reviewText: My students love the way this short video is presented.  It is funny, quick paced and accurate.  It is less than a half hour so it can viewed in one class period too.  Highly recommended!

My son loves this video and the others in the series.  He knows the instruments by name and sound and loves to pretend he is playing along with all the instruments.  It isn't my favorite video, but I have learned a thing or two from them.
